- No no no. I swear I don't know

967
01:12:31.900 --> 01:12:35.822
He literally locked up our memory
and I cannot remember

968
01:12:35.823 --> 01:12:38.850
Nobody can But. I do know this..

969
01:12:38.885 --> 01:12:43.360
He'll do anything to keep her from racing
because if she crosses the finish line...

970
01:12:43.529 --> 01:12:46.661
the game will reset
and she won't be a glitch anymore

971
01:12:46.697 --> 01:12:48.309
Where is she now?

972
01:12:48.310 --> 01:12:49.920
- In the Fungeon with Fix-It Felix.
- Felix??

973
01:12:49.955 --> 01:12:52.411
I'm sorry. that's all I know
that's all I know. I swear

974
01:12:52.480 --> 01:12:56.831
No please don't put me back
in your filthy mouth again

975
01:12:58.949 --> 01:13:03.625
Stick around
- Yes. okay I will. I will.. thank you

976
01:13:07.222 --> 01:13:09.005
C'mon I know you're out there

977
01:13:10.201 --> 01:13:13.519
Saccharin saturated nightmare

978
01:13:17.400 --> 01:13:19.531
Where?

979
01:13:34.847 --> 01:13:39.850
Doomsday and Armageddon just had
a baby. and it is ugly

980
01:13:41.880 --> 01:13:46.522
Hello. hello... somebody?
Anybody?

981
01:13:46.523 --> 01:13:49.155
Please let me out

982
01:13:49.988 --> 01:13:54.296
What is that.. what he says...?
I'm gonna wreck it

983
01:13:57.533 --> 01:14:00.817
Why do I fix everything I touch?

984
01:14:04.596 --> 01:14:08.320
Felix
- Ralph. I'm so glad to see you

985
01:14:08.882 --> 01:14:12.643
No. wait.. I'm not
What do you have to say for yourself?

986
01:14:12.678 --> 01:14:15.811
Wait. I don't want to hear
I'm not talking to you

987
01:14:15.846 --> 01:14:17.397
Okay. don't talk That's fine

988
01:14:17.432 --> 01:14:19.427
But you have to fix this go-cart
for me pronto

989
01:14:19.527 --> 01:14:22.964
I don't have to do boo
Forgive my potty mouth

990
01:14:23.000 --> 01:14:25.995
I'm just so..
so crossed with you

991
01:14:26.361 --> 01:14:28.375
Do you have any idea
what you put me through?

992
01:14:28.410 --> 01:14:31.314
I were in Hickelty pickelty
all over creation looking

993
01:14:31.315 --> 01:14:34.218
for you. I almost drowned
in chocolate milk mix

994
01:14:34.261 --> 01:14:38.072
And then. I met the most dynamite gal

995
01:14:38.100 --> 01:14:41.845
Oh.. she gives me the
honey glow. something aweful

996
01:14:41.880 --> 01:14:47.161
But. she rebuff my affections
And then. I got thrown in jail

997
01:14:47.196 --> 01:14:48.696
Felix. pull yourself together

998
01:14:48.731 --> 01:14:54.086
No. Ralph you don't know what it's like to
be rejected and treated like a criminal

999
01:14:54.460 --> 01:14:57.755
Yes. I do That's everyday in my life

1000
01:14:58.386 --> 01:15:01.171
It is?
- Which is why I ran off

1001
01:15:01.206 --> 01:15:03.373
I try to be a good guy but I'm not

1002
01:15:03.408 --> 01:15:06.386
Just a bad guy and I need your help

1003
01:15:06.421 --> 01:15:08.557
There's a little girl
whose only hope is this cart

1004
01:15:08.592 --> 01:15:10.505
Please. Felix fix it

1005
01:15:10.933 --> 01:15:14.116
And I promise I will never try
to be good again

1006
01:15:37.654 --> 01:15:40.220
I know. I know. I know I'm an idiot

1007
01:15:40.686 --> 01:15:43.927
And?
- and a real Numbskull

1008
01:15:43.962 --> 01:15:46.933
And?
- a selfish diaper baby.

1009
01:15:46.968 --> 01:15:51.351
And?
- and.. a Stinkbrain.

1010
01:15:51.386 --> 01:15:54.537
The stinkiest brain ever

1011
01:16:16.696 --> 01:16:22.031
My sweet subjects. I came without a
flinch of hesitation to show you

1012
01:16:22.170 --> 01:16:25.016
that I have never been
so happy in all my life

1013
01:16:25.051 --> 01:16:27.323
to say the following words

1014
01:16:27.554 --> 01:16:31.234
Let the Random Roster Race commence

1015
01:16:47.767 --> 01:16:50.743
Okay. remember.. you don't
have to win Just cross

1016
01:16:50.744 --> 01:16:53.718
that finish line and
you'll be a real racer

1017
01:16:53.806 --> 01:16:55.723
I'm already a real racer

1018
01:16:58.292 --> 01:17:00.544
And I'm gonna win

1019
01:17:23.769 --> 01:17:25.299
Power Up.

1020
01:17:32.847 --> 01:17:35.010
Oh..
A La Mode.

1021
01:17:38.707 --> 01:17:40.757
Sweet Seekers.

1022
01:17:40.912 --> 01:17:43.214
Have some candy

1023
01:18:00.770 --> 01:18:05.140
Behind you..
Infront of you..

1024
01:18:12.049 --> 01:18:15.203
It's the glitch
- The glitch

1025
01:18:15.239 --> 01:18:17.705
Light 'em up Candlehead

1026
01:18:20.454 --> 01:18:23.741
What's this?
Cherry Bomb.

1027
01:18:30.407 --> 01:18:33.582
I told you
You're just an accident waiting to happen

1028
01:18:51.069 --> 01:18:52.876
My candle...

1029
01:18:53.668 --> 01:18:56.429
Alright. gotta keep it under control

1030
01:18:56.491 --> 01:18:58.645
No more glitching

1031
01:18:59.342 --> 01:19:02.822
Okay kid. let's finish this thing
without any more surprises

1032
01:19:03.717 --> 01:19:05.936
Hope you're happy jump-pile

1033
01:19:05.971 --> 01:19:08.953
This game is going down and
it's all your fault

1034
01:19:08.988 --> 01:19:11.657
My lady. you came back
- Canned it. Fix-It.

1035
01:19:11.811 --> 01:19:14.797
That Cy-Bug you brought with you
multiplied

1036
01:19:14.832 --> 01:19:18.075
No. it died in the taffy swamp
believe me

1037
01:19:20.531 --> 01:19:23.020
You're wrong!

1038
01:19:28.931 --> 01:19:33.125
Listen up people.
head to Game Central Station. now..

1039
01:19:33.247 --> 01:19:35.224
Move it let's go let's go

1040
01:19:45.142 --> 01:19:46.813
No

1041
01:20:27.535 --> 01:20:32.795
Get off of my track
- hey. what are you crazy?

1042
01:20:33.394 --> 01:20:38.408
I forbid you to cross that finish line

1043
01:20:39.585 --> 01:20:42.202
Knock it out

1044
01:20:43.345 --> 01:20:47.788
Ralph. look
- Kid...

1045
01:20:49.618 --> 01:20:54.451
No. Stop it. - Let me.. urgh!!
- Not letting you undo all my hard work

1046
01:20:56.672 --> 01:20:58.797
Is that....

1047
01:21:00.281 --> 01:21:02.783
No way....

1048
01:21:03.652 --> 01:21:07.408
What the... Who are you??
- I'm Turbo

1049
01:21:07.447 --> 01:21:09.807
The greatest racer ever

1050
01:21:09.992 --> 01:21:13.071
And I did not reprogram
this world to let you

1051
01:21:13.106 --> 01:21:17.897
and that holocust riddled warhock
take it away from me

1052
01:21:19.449 --> 01:21:21.046
Turbotastic

1053
01:21:21.471 --> 01:21:24.136
End of the line. glitch

1054
01:21:24.840 --> 01:21:27.469
Glitch. That's it

1055
01:21:27.569 --> 01:21:30.904
C'mon. Vanellope. I know you said
you wouldn't do it again...

1056
01:21:30.939 --> 01:21:35.692
But you're gonna do it one more time
Just focus and concentrate

1057
01:21:35.727 --> 01:21:39.302
And..
Glitch.

1058
01:21:39.430 --> 01:21:41.839
No

1059
01:21:42.808 --> 01:21:47.606
Sweet mother of monkey milk I did it

1060
01:21:47.792 --> 01:21:50.041
No

1061
01:21:54.833 --> 01:21:58.370
Bring it home kid
The finish line's wide open

1062
01:22:12.590 --> 01:22:15.161
No

1063
01:22:15.502 --> 01:22:17.072
Kid. kid are you okay?

1064
01:22:17.107 --> 01:22:19.453
I'm fine. I'm fine
Let's finish this race

1065
01:22:24.313 --> 01:22:27.391
Oh my randd!!
- Alright C'mon we gotta get out of here

1066
01:22:27.426 --> 01:22:31.057
But I didn't cross the finish line
- There is no finish line

1067
01:22:31.782 --> 01:22:34.460
Move it or lose it people
c'mon everybody out now

1068
01:22:36.774 --> 01:22:39.449
Ralph. it's not gonna work
- We gotta try

1069
01:22:43.651 --> 01:22:45.949
Kid
- Ralph I told you I can't leave the game

1070
01:22:46.516 --> 01:22:48.852
C'mon
- Ralph. just stop

1071
01:22:49.643 --> 01:22:53.351
It's gotta work
- Stop. it's no use

1072
01:23:01.920 --> 01:23:04.283
It's okay. Ralph.

1073
01:23:05.677 --> 01:23:09.240
Alright Fix-It. that's everyone
now we gotta blow up this exit

1074
01:23:11.757 --> 01:23:14.243
Just go. go without me

1075
01:23:15.057 --> 01:23:17.619
What about this game?
- Nothing we can do about it

1076
01:23:17.654 --> 01:23:21.782
Without a beacon. there's no way
to stop these monsters

1077
01:23:25.045 --> 01:23:28.799
Beacon..
stay with Felix

1078
01:23:29.237 --> 01:23:32.122
Let me borrow that thing lady
- Ralph. where are you going?

1079
01:23:32.157 --> 01:23:34.258
I got some wrecking to do

1080
01:23:34.357 --> 01:23:37.088
I'll meet you at the finish line
- No. wait

1081
01:23:37.123 --> 01:23:39.104
Fix-It. get behind me

1082
01:23:58.805 --> 01:24:00.383
One more..

1083
01:24:02.664 --> 01:24:06.343
Welcome to the Boss Level
- Turbo.

1084
01:24:07.137 --> 01:24:13.949
Because of you. Ralph. I'm now
the most powerful virus in the Arcade

1085
01:24:14.363 --> 01:24:16.333
I can take over any game I want

1086
01:24:16.368 --> 01:24:20.773
I should thank you
but.. it'd be more fun to kill you

1087
01:24:22.550 --> 01:24:25.074
Get back here little guy

1088
01:24:33.439 --> 01:24:35.472
Where do you think you're going?

1089
01:24:39.854 --> 01:24:42.072
I'm not through with you yet

1090
01:24:42.107 --> 01:24:44.290
Up we go
- No

1091
01:24:50.319 --> 01:24:53.024
Fall back

1092
01:24:53.940 --> 01:24:56.433
Kid

1093
01:25:02.404 --> 01:25:04.593
Look at that. it's your little friend

1094
01:25:05.434 --> 01:25:08.460
Let's watch her die together. shall we

1095
01:25:08.569 --> 01:25:10.536
No

1096
01:25:11.231 --> 01:25:15.623
It's game over for both of you
- No

1097
01:25:16.181 --> 01:25:18.704
Just for me

1098
01:25:27.259 --> 01:25:30.266
I'm bad. and that's good

1099
01:25:30.943 --> 01:25:34.070
I will never be good and that's not bad

1100
01:25:36.420 --> 01:25:42.309
There's no one I'd rather be..
..than me

1101
01:26:09.982 --> 01:26:14.031
Kid
- Don't worry. I got it under control

1102
01:26:39.631 --> 01:26:43.958
Why are you going into the light...

1103
01:26:44.467 --> 01:26:49.889
No. no..
Yea.

1104
01:26:51.126 --> 01:26:54.834
Go into the light

1105
01:27:01.848 --> 01:27:06.696
Chocolate. it's chocolate
I love chocolate

1106
01:27:07.134 --> 01:27:10.566
Beautiful chocolate

1107
01:27:11.312 --> 01:27:15.180
You did it. Ralph.
Oh..Way to go brother

1108
01:27:21.292 --> 01:27:23.894
I'm... es..

1109
01:27:29.382 --> 01:27:32.514
All fixed
- You ready for this?

1110
01:27:32.549 --> 01:27:34.644
Ready as I'll ever be

1111
01:27:43.367 --> 01:27:46.242
Look at all the magic sparkles

1112
01:28:16.251 --> 01:28:18.657
Now. I remember

1113
01:28:19.632 --> 01:28:24.144
All hail. the rightful ruler
of Sugar Rush.

1114
01:28:24.179 --> 01:28:26.414
Princess Vanellope.

1115
01:28:26.449 --> 01:28:29.242
I remember She's a princess

1116
01:28:29.277 --> 01:28:30.775
That's right

1117
01:28:30.776 --> 01:28:32.272
- We are so sorry about
the way we treated you

1118
01:28:32.307 --> 01:28:33.467
Ya. those were jokes..

1119
01:28:33.502 --> 01:28:37.087
See. I was just doing
what Taffyta told me to

1120
01:28:37.122 --> 01:28:42.026
Tat tat! as your merciful princess
I hereby decree that

1121
01:28:42.162 --> 01:28:47.265
everyone who has ever
mean to be shall be...

1122
01:28:47.300 --> 01:28:49.887
..executed
- What?

1123
01:28:49.922 --> 01:28:52.269
No no no. please please
- Oh my lamnd

1124
01:28:52.304 --> 01:28:54.775
Oh this place just got interesting

1125
01:28:55.157 --> 01:28:58.025
I don't wanna die
- I'm just kidding

1126
01:28:58.060 --> 01:29:00.596
You are?
- Stop crying. Taffyta.

1127
01:29:00.631 --> 01:29:02.976
I'm trying but..
it won't stop

1128
01:29:03.747 --> 01:29:06.806
Wow.. so this is
the real you?

1129
01:29:07.577 --> 01:29:10.665
Princess..
- Oh. Ralph. what are you nuts?

1130
01:29:10.700 --> 01:29:16.173
C'mon. this isn't me This is me

1131
01:29:17.063 --> 01:29:21.023
Look. the code may say I'm a princess but.
I know who I really am Ralph

1132
01:29:21.058 --> 01:29:24.459
I'm a racer with the greatest
superpower ever

1133
01:29:24.494 --> 01:29:26.079
I was here I was there.

1134
01:29:26.114 --> 01:29:29.083
I was glitching through the wall
I'm not giving that up

1135
01:29:29.741 --> 01:29:34.765
Pardon me for asking but. without a
princess. who's gonna lead us? - Yea who?

1136
01:29:35.564 --> 01:29:41.019
Uh.. me. I'm thinking more along
the lines of a constitutional democracy

1137
01:29:41.054 --> 01:29:44.301
President Vanellope von Schweetz.

1138
01:29:44.351 --> 01:29:46.617
Has a nice ring to it don't you think?

1139
01:29:47.789 --> 01:29:49.944
Fix-It. Wreck-It. the
Arcade's about to open.

1140
01:29:49.945 --> 01:29:52.099
Let's move 'em out

1141
01:29:59.616 --> 01:30:02.627
You know you could just stay here
and live in the castle

1142
01:30:02.662 --> 01:30:05.405
You'd have your own wing
where no one would

1143
01:30:05.440 --> 01:30:08.459
ever complain about you or
treat you bad ever again

1144
01:30:08.495 --> 01:30:10.638
You could be happy

1145
01:30:11.007 --> 01:30:13.153
I'm already happy

1146
01:30:13.188 --> 01:30:15.703
Got the coolest friend in the world

1147
01:30:15.972 --> 01:30:18.889
And besides. I've got a job to do too

1148
01:30:18.924 --> 01:30:22.218
May not be as fancy as
being president...

1149
01:30:22.253 --> 01:30:25.617
but it's my duty And it's a big duty

1150
01:30:26.621 --> 01:30:28.836
Ralph. you coming brother?

1151
01:30:30.034 --> 01:30:32.845
See you later. president Fartfeathers.

1152
01:30:32.912 --> 01:30:36.466
Au revoir. admiral Underpants.

1153
01:30:36.649 --> 01:30:39.422
And farewell. bareness Boogerface.

1154
01:30:39.457 --> 01:30:41.808
Goodbye. major Bodyodour.

1155
01:30:41.841 --> 01:30:44.324
Hasta la vista.

1156
01:30:44.460 --> 01:30:46.792
Ralph..
- Alright. to be continued

1157
01:31:01.071 --> 01:31:03.446
I'm gonna wreck it

1158
01:31:04.334 --> 01:31:07.541
Hey. Ralph's back Isn't it great?

1159
01:31:08.130 --> 01:31:11.941
The game's all here
- So. I'm happy to report...

1160
01:31:12.151 --> 01:31:16.571
and you'll be happy to hear
I'm taking life one game at a time

1161
01:31:18.204 --> 01:31:20.625
First. the job hasn't change

1162
01:31:20.660 --> 01:31:25.244
But. news flash..
The Nicelanders are being nice to me

1163
01:31:25.530 --> 01:31:29.127
And you know that got me thinking about
those poor guys left without a game

1164
01:31:29.776 --> 01:31:31.817
So here's what we did
- We're going to wreck it!

1165
01:31:31.852 --> 01:31:34.494
We ask them to help us out
in the bonus level

1166
01:31:34.883 --> 01:31:36.400
We can fix it!

1167
01:31:36.658 --> 01:31:39.968
I'm tellin' you guys. we haven't been
this popular in years

1168
01:31:40.003 --> 01:31:44.657
It's crazy The gamers say we're Retro

1169
01:31:44.692 --> 01:31:47.237
which... It means...
Old.. but Cool

1170
01:31:47.272 --> 01:31:48.566
How come I never noticed this game

1171
01:31:48.601 --> 01:31:52.109
Oh and I decided that living in
a dump wasn't making me feel very good

1172
01:31:52.144 --> 01:31:56.821
So. I cleaned it up. built myself a little
shack and a couple for the new guys too

1173
01:31:57.420 --> 01:32:00.535
Well. with a little help from Felix

1174
01:32:00.570 --> 01:32:03.977
Oh and guess who is the best man
at his and Calhoun's wedding?

1175
01:32:04.012 --> 01:32:07.206
That's right my friend
Old ham hands himself

1176
01:32:07.430 --> 01:32:10.786
Very elegant affair.
should've seen her. lot of grandeur.

1177
01:32:10.821 --> 01:32:13.143
And not a single bug

1178
01:32:16.435 --> 01:32:20.227
And let's just say
some tears were shed.

1179
01:32:21.560 --> 01:32:25.296
But I gotta say.
the best part of my day...

1180
01:32:25.331 --> 01:32:27.537
is when I get thrown off the roof...

1181
01:32:28.835 --> 01:32:31.277
because when the Nicelanders lift me up..

1182
01:32:31.901 --> 01:32:34.453
I get a perfect view of Sugar Rush

1183
01:32:34.983 --> 01:32:37.207
And I can see Vanellope racing

1184
01:32:41.071 --> 01:32:42.774
The kid's a natural..

1185
01:32:42.975 --> 01:32:46.024
And the players love her glitch and all

1186
01:32:46.222 --> 01:32:48.218
Just like I knew they would

1187
01:32:49.206 --> 01:32:53.287
Turns out I don't need a medal
to tell me I'm a good guy

1188
01:32:54.157 --> 01:32:56.946
Cause. if that little kid likes me...

1189
01:32:59.907 --> 01:33:02.250
How bad can I be?

1190
01:33:07.036 --> 01:33:12.548
Sub by: maXeer
~~ MC ~~

1190
01:33:13.305 --> 01:34:13.393
